<hymn_number>716</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 yī shēng de biāo gān shì róng yào zhǔ de míng. yī shēng de biāo gān yào tǎo fù shén xǐ yuè.
 yī shēng de biāo gān yào zuò gè hǎo pū rén. yī shēng de biāo gān shě jǐ yào dāng xiān.
 xiàng shù zhī zài fēng zhōng hū huàn chūn tiān, wǒ men dōu yǒu hěn zhēn chéng de xīn yuàn.
 yī shēng de biāo gān huó chū jī dū, shì wǒ yī shēng de biāo gān, yī shēng de biāo gān.</lyrics>
<title>yī shēng de biāo gān 迦南716</title>
</song>